Priority: extra
Maintainer: Michael Zanetti <michael.zanetti@canonical.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), libindicate-qt-dev, pkg-config, qt4-qmake, libqt4-dev, qtbase, qtdeclarative, libxpathselect-dev, mesa-common-dev, libgl1-mesa-dev, libgles2-mesa-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
Section: libs
