Package: autopilot-qt
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: python-autopilot
Description: This project makes Qt4 applications introspectable by autopilot.
 This allows autopilot to test any existing Qt4 application, 
 without having to rebuild the application under test.

